### **4. 33_ChartRippleView**  
**Description:**  
Renders real-time numeric data into a scrolling chart with wave-style animations.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# ChartRippleView - Realtime Streaming Line Graph

ChartRippleView is a tool to visualize any continuous data stream with smooth, ripple-style chart animations.

## Features
- Scrollable real-time graph  
- Adjustable refresh speed  
- Matplotlib-powered  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/33_ChartRippleView.git
cd 33_ChartRippleView
python visualize.py
